data.meta_description:
#warthunder #live_wt #workshop

MERDEC Universal Camos
MERDEC was the first universal vehicle camo used by NATO (at least I think it was, might have been just US) through the late 70\'s and early 80\'s, until it was replace by the NATO CARC Three-Tones sometime around the late 80\'s. This website I based these off of has more of the history as well and good resources if you\'re interested.
https://www.onthewaymodels.com/articles/MERDECcamouflage.htm
Edit 1: I fixed the decal on black bug (thanks @Schindibee) and also added Arctic, which I originally excluded b/c it\'s just all white, but it was MERDEC and I figured some people
